title: Amber Seed Team - Looking for Top Laner
body:
{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}} 

Hey guys and girls, 

Amber Seed is looking for a Top laner (or possibly mid) to join our team, preferably plat and above.

if you are interested fill out the form below, if you are below the rank mentioned and enthusiastic you may still apply!

https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1LnQ8MHs9jF_YlqCumF6EgrK6imLhjxWcz_mMTGMukB4

Thanks!
